   <body>
      <context>You can post a comment on a document and associate a reference number with the comment. The date the comment is posted is also recorded.</context>
      <ol>
         <li href="../../../Warehouse/Task_Warehouse/AcsPrjContDocsNav.dita#task-5739/AccProContDocFolder">
            <p/>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select a document, and then click <uicontrol>Comment Log</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>COMMENT LOG </uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <title>Comment Log</title>
                  <image href="../../CoSP/Document_Management/Screenshot/Comment_Log.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Add</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>A row is added to the comment log list.</p>
            <p>The date the comment is posted, and the user name of the user posting the comment are displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the added row, double-click in the <uicontrol>Comments </uicontrol>column, and enter comments for the document.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the added row, double-click in the <uicontrol>Reference Number </uicontrol>column, and enter a reference number for the comment.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
